Best Red Carpet Dresses at Fashion Week Fall 2017 This Chanel Dress Has Kirsten Dunst's Name Written All Over It March 7, 2017   This Chanel Dress Has Kirsten Dunst's Name Written All Over It 
Our favorite actress and icons can do without their stylists for the next couple of months. Rest assured, we're here to dress them for the red carpet . While tracking the runways in Europe this Fashion Month , we immediately spotted looks that belong on our favorite celebs. Whether it's because they've shopped the label once before or are total brand devotees, this is how we imagine Kirsten Dunst , Rosie Huntington-Whiteley, Amal Clooney, Kendall Jenner, Emily Ratajkowski, and more are stocking their wardrobes come Fall â€” or maybe even before that, if they're lucky .
